race.comment: EXPECTANT (2) was close up at Eagle Farm and again at Doomben following. Maps well and is well placed to be winning in this grade with a 3kg claimer aboard. WHISKY DREAM (3) raced well in a number of city contests last preparation over this trip and has needed the two sprint runs this time in. She'll be much better today stepping up in trip and should be in the finish. MEDICAL AUTOCRAT (6) is another who'll appreciate the longer journey. May need one more but his best is good enough. The veteran CHASING JACKLEY (5) has kicked off his latest campaign nicely. Showed good improvement second up at Warwick. ELLA TE AMA (1) is another who'd be a contender finding his best form.
